# Documentation Guidelines

## Template Instructions

**To Use This Template:**
1. Replace `[PROJECT_NAME]` with your actual project name
2. Replace `[PROJECT_TYPE]` with your project type (web app, library, CLI tool, etc.)
3. Update the document types section with your specific documentation needs
